Ewaki Petero o Yohana enkiguana


1  Ore eirorie Petero o Yohana olorere nepuonu ilapolosak o lkitok loo larripok le nkaji e Nkai o Sadukayo enetii ninche. 
2  Netagorote enkaraki naiteng'enita ilkipaareta olorere aaliki te Yesu empiunoto o lootuata. 
3  Neibung ninche aapik jela o mekenyu, amu emuto ina kata. 
4  Kake eiruko ilkumok le lelo ootoning'o ilo rorei; nebaya lewa anaa nkalifuni imiet.


5  Ore taaisere neiturrurro larikok o lpayiani loo Lyahudi, o laiteng'enak loo nkitanapat te nebo te Yerusalem. 
6  Netii etii Olapolosani Kitok oji Ananias, netii Kaiafas, o Yohana o Aleksanta o kulikae ake lo lmarei lo Lapolosani Kitok. 
7  Neitasheyie lelo kipaareta te dukuya ninche neikilikuan aajoki, “Kaji intae nkuna pee itaasa ena? Kaa golon ena niatata, naa keneng'ae enkarna nitaasishore?” 
8  Ore eiganya Petero Enkiyang'et Sinyati, newaliki ajoki, “Lo kituaak lo lorere, o lpayiani, 
9  te naa taa keikilikuanishoreki iyiook te le kekun te mbae supat naitaasaki oltung'ani maima o eneikuna pee eishiunyeki ele tung'ani, 
10  neishiaakino te niyiolouwu intae pooki, neishiaakino neyiolou olorere pooki le Israeli nchere, ore pee eitashe ele tung'ani te dukuya intae aa biyoto katukul, enkaraki engolon e nkarna e Yesu Kristo le Nasareti lishomo intae aashe neitopiwuo Enkai ninye aitung'uaa ilootuata. 
11   Yesu eimakita lkigerot pee ejo, ‘Ilo soit litemenaitie intae ilashetak otaa osoit kitok lo lmairroto.’ 
12  Meetae tukul likae otumieki enjeunoto, nemeetae ai arna naishoruno ti abori shumata, naishooki ltung'ana pee kijeunye.”


13  Ore pee edol Enkiguana ina natishirrakita Petero o Yohana, nemusu aajo ltung'ana ake ninche lemeeta enkisuma nashomo, neme ng'eni sii, neing'asia; neyiolou aajo ninche lapa ooisiritore Yesu. 
14  Ore enkaraki nadolita ilo tung'ani oishiunyeki eitashe te nebo ninche, nelau enawaliki. 
15  Kake ore pee eitanap ninche meipung'o te nkaji e nkiguana, neiteru lpayiani aaiguana oopeny, 
16  ejo kuna, “Kaa kintaas kulo tung'ana? Amu eibale ake ninye too ltung'ana pooki oomanya Yerusalem nchere ninche etaasishoreki te na bae naba nji e nking'asia, nimikiindim sii aatomiki. 
17  Kake ore naa pee meitadarari ena bae ti atua olorere, maing'odia, nikirishie kulo tung'ana pee meigil aairorie likae tung'ani te na arna.” 
18  Neipotu ninche neitanap nereiki aajoki pee meigil ake aairorie aashu eiteng'en likae tung'ani te nkarna e Yesu. 
19  Kake etawalikitia Petero o Yohana aajoki ninche, “Entirish intae o openy enaishiaakino te Nkai, te naa ai intae kining ana ke Nkai. 
20  Amu mikiindim ake iyiook aatapal mikilimu inikitoduaa o nikitoning'o.” 
21  Neitoki ake ina kiguana aaing'ode ninche neitirrishaki oleng, neitoki aaisho epuo. Etalaita taa katukul enaitameyie ninche amu errepita ltung'ana pooki Enkai te ina nataasaki. 
22  Amu ore ilo tung'ani oitaasaki ina e nking'asia aaishiunye neitogiroyie larin artam.

Etoomono lairukok Enkai meishoo empijan nairorie


23  Ore pee eing'ueikini ninche, nepuonu enetii lchoreta lenye, nelikioo nena pooki naatiaakita ninche ilapolosak kituaak o lpayiani. 
24   Neisho ninche pee ening nena, neilepie tenebo iltoiloishi lenye aailepakinye Enkai ejo: “Olaitoriani, oitobira shumata o enkop o enaiposha, o nena pooki naatii, 
25   naa iyie oirorie Papa lang Daudi ilo sinka lino, te Nkiyang'et Sinyati, pee ejo,

‘Aainyo pee epush Iloreren leme Lyahudi,

neipiru ltung'ana enkiguana nemeaku?


26  Etanapate laiguanak kituaak le nkop,

nesoto laitoriak te nebo, aa Olaitoriani Enkai earare,

o ilo lenye otubulokoki eilata aaput.’


27   Amu esipa nchere tiatua ena anasa apa esotokinoi Osinka lino Yesu, osinka lino sinyati laa ninye itubukoko eilata aput, ninye etasotokinote Herode o Pontio Pilato o Loreren leme Lyahudi o ltung'ana le Israel, 
28  pee eitaas enapake naidipa magilanisho ino o enkiguana ino makewan atejo keaku. 
29  Ore naa taata, Olaitoriani, toduaa iyie ina king'odia enye, nincho isinkan linono meiroro te ororei lino mpijan pooki; 
30  nintorioo iyie enkaina ino aishiunye olorere; ninchoru metaasi ilmonek o mbaa e nking'asia te nkarna e Yesu, Osinka lino sinyati.” 
31  Ore pee eomon neigirigiro ine netumore, neiput ninche pooki Enkiyang'et Sinyati neshirraki aairo ororei le Nkai.

Etang'ara ilairukok imasaa enye


32   Neaku lelo pooki ooiruko ilo ltau obo o le yieunoto nabo, nemeetae olojo nkunenyena masaa naata, amu etang'ara ninche ntokitin pooki naata. 
33  Nelimu ilkipaareta te ngolon shakenisho e mpiunoto o Laitoriani Yesu; nelotu empiris e Nkai shumata ninche pooki. 
34  Nemeetae hoo obo te ninche olau toki, amu ore lelo apa ooata masaa oo nkurman aashu inoo nkajijik, nemir neyau mpesai naainosieki nena masaa, 
35  neirragie too nkejek oo lkipaareta pee eorikini pooki tung'ani, anaa naabaiki.


36  Neetae Yosef, oishoo lkipaareta enkarna aajo Barnabas (kejo ina oloitagol ilkulikae oishuaa) naa oloo Lewi, laa ole nkop e Kipros, 
37  neaku eeta ninye enkurma, nemir, neyau iropiyiani naainosie, neirragie too nkejek oo lkipaareta.

